    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Cell 2: Sample Training Data Creation\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"We need training data for our intent classifier. This data represents different types of queries users might ask a library chatbot.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"### Intent Categories (from our knowledge base):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **book_search** - Looking for books by title, author, or subject\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **availability** - Checking if a book is available\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **borrow** - Borrowing or reserving books\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **return** - Returning books\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **library_info** - General library information\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **account** - User account related queries\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **hours** - Library hours and locations\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **identity** - User identity/introduction queries\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Create sample training data for the library chatbot\\n\",\n",
