    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"### Evaluation Metrics Summary:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Accuracy**: How often the model is correct overall\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Precision**: Of predicted positives, how many are correct\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **Recall**: Of actual positives, how many did we find\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- **F1-Score**: Balance between precision and recall (harmonic mean)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"### Architecture Benefits:\\n\",\n",
